	<li><h2>Hack Google search</h2>
	<p>Google indexes a ton of opportunities that you can find by tweaking a few search settings. For example, if you’re interested in responding to RFP’s, search: “RFP website design development filetype:PDF” this will only show PDF documents. Further, you can set your search range to the “past week” to only get recent results. There’s no limit to the amount of links you’ll find on google, so getting specific with keywords, budget, search options, and anything else you can is really going to help.</p>
	
